What are the different media types?

The different media types, as derived from the provided SQL result, include MPEG audio files, Protected AAC audio files, Protected MPEG-4 video files, Purchased AAC audio files, and AAC audio files. Each of these types corresponds to a specific format for encoding audio and video content.
